Class CallHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • CallHistory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumberStack

    public class CallHistory
extends java.lang.Object
implements NumberStack
    A stack of numbers which represents the call history of a phone. Implements the NumberStack interface with one extra method: getLength().
